title: Gold 1 Support LF I2G-P Team or Duo for ranked
body:
Looking for a team to join for the Iron to Gold/Plat online tournaments or a Duo to climb to Diamond with by the end of the season. 

For the duo I am looking for a chill person with a mic.

I do not tilt very easily, if ya interested add me. I will link my OP.GG and champion masteries below.
Thanks for considering.

OP.GG: https://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=DramaticChicken
Champion Mastery: https://championmasterylookup.derpthemeus.com/summoner/?summoner=DramaticChicken&region=OCE

replies.body: Hey mate if you are interested in joining a team add me. We are all plat+ players but we are really just looking for the right kind of person who are willing to learn and enjoys playing as a team.
Sweet, I'll add ya. Sorry It took me a little to respond, got busy.
